	<ThingDef ParentName="Simple">
    <defName>SimpleProstheticLeg</defName>
    <label>simple prosthetic leg</label>
    <description>A leg prosthesis. While it lacks a neutral interface, its complex arrangement of internal joints allows it to mimic natural movement quite convincingly. Still, it is inferior to a real leg.</description>
